<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Jeskola Corpseshredder</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-01-11 07:57:11</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>yes, it is dropped by the Hooded Dhampyre im Mistmoore. he is VERY deep in the dungeon, much harder to get to than the tower even. you have to make your way to the backyard, where many MOB's are (including the Hemo Enologist for the rogue quest for the crappy rapier), and around the side to the "garden/fountain" area. the hooded dhampyre spawns in the furthest back position, and looks similar to butler syncall. very rare spawn</font></td></tr></table>
