<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This cloak is very hard to obtain because of the fact that most people start off KoS in MM. And the fact that you unless you get invis to undead animal and improved camo you have almost no chance of getting down there if you are not a druid or 49+ ranger. I have seen the dhamphyr spawn in MM while I was in GY there and stay on track for a few days before some druid ran up and killed him. I would rather camp a different cloak instead of in the deep bottom of one of the biggest train places in the game. Go for a cloak of shadows if your not a druid or cannot afford this. Longer wait but still worth it<BR>
